




{"id":15932,"date":"2024-09-04T13:28:59","date_gmt":"2024-09-04T06:28:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=15932"},"modified":"2025-04-23T14:03:49","modified_gmt":"2025-04-23T07:03:49","slug":"microphone-da-huong-innosmart-e500","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/microphone-da-huong-innosmart-e500\/","title":{"rendered":"Microphone \u0111a h\u01b0\u1edbng INNOSMART E500"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3>Micro \u0111a h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u00f4ng minh INNOSMART E500<\/h3>\n<p>Micro \u0111a h\u01b0\u1edbng INNOSMART E500 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea5t, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Beamforming ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd \u00e2m thanh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thu \u00e2m xa \u0111\u1ebfn 8 m\u00e9t, E500 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, mang \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh r\u1ea3nh tay hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/p>\n<h3>T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt<\/h3>\n<p>INNOSMART E500 trang b\u1ecb microphone array k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi 10 micro x\u1ebfp theo v\u00f2ng tr\u00f2n, cho ph\u00e9p thu \u00e2m \u0111a h\u01b0\u1edbng 360 \u0111\u1ed9 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong ph\u1ea1m vi 8 m\u00e9t. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Beamforming th\u00edch \u1ee9ng gi\u00fap theo d\u00f5i gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i th\u00f4ng minh, nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c nhau. T\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng \u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu \u00e2m r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u00edch h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u thu\u1eadt to\u00e1n \u00e2m thanh \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n, bao g\u1ed3m gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n th\u00f4ng minh (ANC) v\u00e0 kh\u1eed ti\u1ebfng vang (AEC), \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e2m thanh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 giao ti\u1ebfp tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1eafm v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y qua c\u1ed5ng USB Type-C v\u00e0 audio 3.5mm, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ea7u ra ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9p (k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1, analog).<\/p>\n<h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt<\/h3>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\">Chi ti\u1ebft<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\"><b>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 \u00e2m thanh<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\">\u0110\u1ed9 nh\u1ea1y<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\">-26 dBFS<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\">SNR<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\">&gt;80 dB(A)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\">T\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\">20Hz &#8211; 16KHz<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\">T\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 l\u1ea5y m\u1eabu<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\">32kHz<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\">Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch thu \u00e2m<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\">8 meters<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\">Ch\u1ed1ng vang (AEC)<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\">C\u00f3<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\">Ch\u1ed1ng \u1ed3n (ANC)<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\">C\u00f3<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 43.3784%;\">AGC<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 55.5405%;\">C\u00f3<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=